cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.SI 

The paper deals with multi-modal data fusion using machine learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The specific data sources being fused are optical and SAR data, which are often used in image retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications. The paper also mentions the use of topological data analysis (TDA), which falls under the category of scientific computing (cs.SI).
